<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[55661]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA['El Eclipse', at the Teatre Nacional de Catalunya]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[Xavier Albertí is presenting this piece at the Teatre Nacional de Catalunya (TNC) as part of the line-up for the Grec 2014 summer festival in Barcelona.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>Leonor and Carla decide to get married in the garden of Leonor’s family home to coincide with a astronomical event: a total eclipse that will darken the Earth for several minutes but, at the same time, illuminate the loving future for this couple.</p>
<p>This is the starting point for L’eclipsi, a piece directed by Xavier Albertí and brought to the stage of the Teatre Nacional de Catalunya as part of the Grec festival. Astronomical phenomena also determine the development of music during this spectacular musical.</p>
